      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality masterpiece that has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. This vehicle is in flawless condition, boasting original factory paint with a deep, glass-like finish free of any swirls, chips, or imperfections. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the cabin still retains that distinct 'new car' aroma. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history from authorized specialists and a powertrain that delivers smooth, effortless performance. This is a true time-capsule example, complete with all original keys, manuals, and a spotless title, perfect for the most discerning collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
